        "Heading_size": "h2",
        "Heading_color": "#c0ccbe",
        "title": "ON THE VINES",
        "video-sec-content-txt-1": "<p>With an ideal Mediterranean microclimate, an abundance of soil diversity and water from the life-giving Breede River, the Alvi’s Drift winery vineyards are ideally positioned for producing remarkable South African wines of unique character and complexity.</p><p>Harvested from our prime, older Alvi’s Drift vineyards, the Chardonnay grapes for this wine were grown in the limestone-rich soils found on the banks of the Breede River.</p>",
        "button-txt": "",
        "button_link": "",
